e and agricultural land into settlement zones. These changes are subject to ongoing court cases. The department continues to alter land use classifications on a plot-by-plot basis.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/infrastructure/goa-tcp-designates-58-lakh-sq-meters-as-non-developable-land-to-protect-eco-sensitive-zones/131680462?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-115926/131680462.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "infrastructure"}]}